Package presentation

package presentation
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ApplicationWindow
    Class used to create a window in which There are buttons for client, product, and order windows
    BaseWindow
    Class used to create a window in which There are buttons that open insertWindow of the specific type or viewWindow
    CommandWindow
    Class used to create a window in which There are two jComboBoxes from which we can select a client and a product and also a quantity text field and a button
    insertWindow
    Class used to create a window in which There are generated some fields for the columns of a table in which the employee can enter the data of a new row and commit
    OrderWindow
    Class used to create a window in which There are buttons that open a commandWindow
    viewWindow
    Class used to create a window in which the user sees the current rows from the table and can make changes and/or remove some fields
